{"tid":2140477,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"余慧明質疑內地方艙醫院規格較亞博館現時的社區治療設施更低，料難符合香港標準。","createTime":"2020-08-05T04:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T04:48:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"972ea79263c04647fece763189e825e7ccead322","tid":2140477,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T04:45:10.000Z","msg":"余慧明質疑內地方艙醫院規格較亞博館現時的社區治療設施更低，料難符合香港標準。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/WHFRJZB42F6DQQ2RA7GTIXWIEE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2FWHFRJZB42F6DQQ2RA7GTIXWIEE%2F&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7Zeag7Fv2waV%2FkF2w15sEbuDLw%3D&h=21289288\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2FWHFRJZB42F6DQQ2RA7GTIXWIEE%2F&h=1ead34e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/WHFRJZB42F6DQQ2RA7GTIXWIEE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n內地病床無間隔 交叉感染風險增 <br />\n亞博治療營規格恐遜現狀<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】偉大祖國派員。。。。。。。。。醫管局員工陣線主席余慧明質疑內地方艙醫院規格較亞博館現時的社區治療設施更低，料難符合香港標準。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，支援隊將協助本港興。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/M5VdVCZCVGNDlaSmtnyPW8xkmD4=/1412x515/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/U3ECUIODG4QXL6MGEPSLGIBKJI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FM5VdVCZCVGNDlaSmtnyPW8xkmD4%3D%2F1412x515%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FU3ECUIODG4QXL6MGEPSLGIBKJI.gif&h=be032fec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n武漢客廳方艙醫院內放滿病床，並沒有任何間隔，病人完全沒私隱。新華網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傳設計方案已完成<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：先遣隊訪實驗室 工業園員工抗議<br />\n<br />\n支援隊成員之一、設計。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n文中又透露將改建亞博館展。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n內地方艙醫院一直被質疑病人密集、。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/26F7GcQrXF9f7okHJb_pNe2rnLE=/680x444/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7LOTAX2H63CTYGXONEPVYJLSIU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F26F7GcQrXF9f7okHJb_pNe2rnLE%3D%2F680x444%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7LOTAX2H63CTYGXONEPVYJLSIU.gif&h=b6b349d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n病格設有碌架床，增加交叉感染風險。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n余慧明：料難符合港標準<br />\n<br />\n內地規格。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n余慧明質疑內地方艙醫院的規格較亞博館社區治療設施規格更低，「擺晒啲病床喺度，連獨立病格都唔係」，造成交叉感染風險，若依照內地方艙醫院經驗興建香港臨時醫院，料難符合香港標準，更擔心內地專家需時了解香港標準和需要，需時磨合和遷就，最終因快得慢，倒不如由熟悉香港醫院的本地人員負責，效率更高。<br />\n<br />\n感染及傳染病科。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局總行政經理劉。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"2454e1d283def5e87d65decafbc2b7ba1aa7e3a6","tid":2140477,"uid":44870,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T04:46:04.000Z","msg":"港共好快會放寬本地標準"},{"pid":"801dfb7c2cd59d84930117556e17854d7ec9950e","tid":2140477,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T04:47:59.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"328cb4502f0e542eab194b245d6c84be6dfb623f","tid":2140477,"uid":33060,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T04:48:31.000Z","msg":"到時咪一車車港豬,話你受感染,跟住咪車你入去囉"}]}